headline: ONWARD Medical Appoints Ali Kiboro as Chief Financial Officer
summary: EINDHOVEN, the Netherlands, Jan. 23, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- ONWARD Medical N.V. (Euronext: ONWD – US ADR: ONWRY), the neurotechnology company pioneering spinal cord stimulation therapies to restore movement, function, and independence, today announces the appointment of Ali Kiboro as Chief Financial Officer, effective January 2026.
